    Type for the reasons for blocking a pump

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      ALL_HOSES_BLOCKED
      The Pump is blocked because all Hoses connected to the pump are blocked.
      MANUAL
      The Pump was blocked manually by calling the setBlock method on the pump.
      NOT_BLOCKED
      The Pump is not blocked.
      STOPPED
      The pump has been blocked due to a Stop or an Stop.

        public static final PumpBlockedReasons ALL_HOSES_BLOCKED
